# zeroclaw doctor

> Run diagnostics for ZeroClaw daemon, scheduler, and channel freshness.
> More information: <https://github.com/zeroclaw-labs/zeroclaw#quick-start>.

- Run diagnostics:

`zeroclaw doctor`

- Display help:

`zeroclaw doctor {{[-h|--help]}}`
